File size
    - du -sk <file>
    - du -sh <file>
    - ls -lh <file>

Archiving files
    - tar -cf  - archive and name the file
    - tar -tf - show all the files in the tar 
    - tar -xf - extract the files
    - tar -zcf - compress it further

    Compressing and Uncompressing
    
    Compress 
        -bzip2
        -gzip
        -xz
    Uncompress
        -bunzip2
        -gunzip
        -unxz

    To view compressed files
        -zcat 
        -bzcat
        -xzcat
